Package com.fssa.freshnest.model

Class Invite

java.lang.Object
com.fssa.freshnest.model.Invite
public class Invite extends Object
Represents an invitation entity that contains information about an invitation event, including its type, date, time, participants, and associated actions. This class provides constructors and methods to manage different aspects of an invitation.
Author:
SusikumarPitchaimuth
